msgstr "**问：如何解决 ValueError：Tokenizer class TokenizersBackend does not exist or is not currently imported？**"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM5.md:1380
msgid "A: Please update the version of transformers to 5.2.0"
msgstr "答：请将 transformers 版本升级到 5.2.0"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM5.md:1382
msgid "**Q: How to enable function calling for GLM-5?**"
